T02D1946:72a-1: krishna ya m'a ri buddha s'a dha nam n'a ma /
T02D1946:72a-3: sangs rgyas gshin rje gshed nag po sgrub pa'i thabs zhes bya ba /
T02D1946:72a-4: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D1946:72a-5: bla ma rje btsun bla med dang //
T02D1946:72a-6: sku gsum mgon po gshegs nyid las //
T02D1946:72a-7: btud de de nyid sgrub pa'i thabs //
T02D1946:72a-8: blo dman bdag gis bshad par bya //
T02D1946:72a-9: sngags pa blo dang ldan pa yis //
T02D1946:72a-10: snying rje chen po rab bskyed de //
T02D1946:72a-11: skad cig dran pas gsal bar bya //
T02D1946:72a-12: gnyis pas rdzogs pa thig le che //
T02D1946:72a-13: bzang po nyid dang dpal gyi mgon //
T02D1946:72a-14: so so las kyang bzhi 'byung bya //
T02D1946:72a-15: rdzogs dang rab tu gnas pa dang ;
T02D1946:72a-16: / mngon par btud la mchod byas te //
T02D1946:72a-17: ya yig sprul pa'i las bya'o //
T02D1946:72a-18: bshags dang rjes su yi rang dang //
T02D1946:72a-19: bskul dang gsol ba gdab pa dang //
T02D1946:72a-20: skyabs su 'gro dang sems bskyed che //
T02D1946:72a-21: lus dbul yongs su bsngo ba bya'o //
T02D1946:72a-22: smon lam gdab dang gshegs su gsol //
T02D1946:72a-23: tshangs pa'i gnas bzhi sngon song bas //
T02D1946:72a-24: rnam thar gsum gyi bdag nyid bsgom //
T02D1946:72a-25: aom sv'a bh'a shuddha dharm'a: bh'a wa shuddho& ham /
T02D1946:72a-26: gnas dang dag pa'i ngo bo dang //
T02D1946:72a-27: bde ba bzang po 'di bsgom bya //
T02D1946:72a-28: sh'u n+ya t'a dzny'a na badzra sva bha wa a'atma ko& ham /
T02D1946:72a-29: sku gsung thugs kyi bdag nyid ni //
T02D1946:72a-30: yi ge gsum gyi ngo bor blta //
T02D1946:72a-31: dag pa'i thig le nam mkha' yi //
T02D1946:72a-32: rgyun gyis gnas pa'i nyi ma h'um //
T02D1946:72a-33: gyur pa rdo rje gzhal med khang //
T02D1946:72a-34: zla ba rdo rje'i sbyor ba yis //
T02D1946:72a-35: chos kyi 'byung gnas rnam par gnas //
T02D1946:72a-36: sna tshogs padma'i dkyil nyid du //
T02D1946:72a-37: zla ba yi ge bcu drug bcas //
T02D1946:72a-38: re pha las byung gnyis pa las //
T02D1946:72a-39: gsal byed yi ge khor yug blta //
T02D1946:72b-0: @72b ro mnyam pa la sa bon nyid //
T02D1946:72b-1: nor bu rdo rje spro dang bsdu //
T02D1946:72b-2: nga rgyal gyur pas rdo rje sems //
T02D1946:72b-3: dkar dang gnag dang dmar ba'i zhal //
T02D1946:72b-4: shes rab gnyis med sgeg dang stangs //
T02D1946:72b-5: gdug dang dur khrod rgyan gyis spras //
T02D1946:72b-6: gri gug thod pa rtsa ba'i phyag / rdo rje ral gri g-yas na bsnams //
T02D1946:72b-7: g-yon na 'khor lo chu skyes so //
T02D1946:72b-8: sa bon 'od kyi bdag nyid dpal //
T02D1946:72b-9: rjes su gyur pas khu bar blta //
T02D1946:72b-10: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje gnas //
T02D1946:72b-11: nyi ma dmar po ya gcig bcas //
T02D1946:72b-12: gyur pas rdo rje sngon po ste //
T02D1946:72b-13: sa bon 'od las gshin rje gshed //
T02D1946:72b-14: char sprin gzhon nu lta bu'i mdog / g-yas pa zla ba lta bu ste //
T02D1946:72b-15: g-yon pa padma r'a ga'i mdog / rang gi yum dang ldan pa'i sku //
T02D1946:72b-16: rtsa ba'i phyag gis 'khyud pa'i stangs //
T02D1946:72b-17: rdo rje ral gri 'khor lo dang //
T02D1946:72b-19: gri gug rdo rje mtshan pa dang //
T02D1946:72b-20: thod pa byang chub sems bkang ba //
T02D1946:72b-21: yum dang mtshungs par 'dzin pa ste //
T02D1946:72b-22: gcer bu rgyan bral skra grol ba'o //
T02D1946:72b-23: snyoms par 'jug pa'i stangs dang ldan //
T02D1946:72b-24: brgya phyed mgo bo'i phreng ba can //
T02D1946:72b-25: padma zla ba'i gdan stengs su //
T02D1946:72b-26: ma he nyi ma gnas pa'i stengs //
T02D1946:72b-27: rdo rje gshed po bsgom par bya //
T02D1946:72b-28: sku gsung thugs dang ldan pa yis //
T02D1946:72b-29: sems dpa'i rdo rje bde bar bsgom //
T02D1946:72b-30: skye mched zla ba'i dkyil 'khor te //
T02D1946:72b-31: sems dpa'i yi ge gsal bar bya //
T02D1946:72b-32: kshim dzim kham gam kam sam //
T02D1946:72b-33: spyi gtsug mgrin pa snying ga'i steng //
T02D1946:72b-34: zla ba padma nyid ma'i dkyil //
T02D1946:72b-35: dkar dmar gnag pa'i yi ge dgong //
T02D1946:72b-37: sa bon las 'phros gshin rje gshed //
T02D1946:72b-38: yab yum gnyis med sbyor ba yis //
T02D1946:72b-39: bde chen byang chub sems kyi rgyun //
T02D1946:72b-40: phab ste spyi gtsug bab gyur pas //
T02D1946:72b-41: dri med dag pas rdo rje sems //
T02D1946:72b-42: spros dang bsdus pas de nyid don //
T02D1946:72b-43: mnyes par byas la rgyud la bstim //
T02D1946:72b-44: nges dang gsal dang brtan pa dang //
T02D1946:72b-45: phab la thig le thig le che //
T02D1946:72b-46: byed pa sbyor dang phra ma dang //
T02D1946:72b-47: go rims nam mkha'i rdo rje'o //
T02D1946:72b-49: rang bzhin nyid nas rdo rje sems //
T02D1946:72b-50: rdo rje nam mkha'i khams sbyor bas //
T02D1946:72b-51: gnyis med ye shes chos kyi sku //
T02D1946:72b-53: ldang ba s'a lu'i 'bras ltar du //
T02D1946:72b-54: gnas pa rgyal po'i dbang bsgyur zhing //
T02D1946:72b-55: dbyings kyi rdo rje tha mi dang //
T02D1946:73a-2: sa stengs sa 'og sa bla yi //
T02D1946:73a-3: gnas su sku gsung thugs bsams te //
T02D1946:73a-4: ma yengs don grub bzlas par bya //
T02D1946:73a-5: aom k'a la r'u pa h'um /
T02D1946:73a-6: 'dis ni brgya byin la sogs pa brgyal bar byed pa'o //
T02D1946:73a-11: ya da yo ni: ra ya kshe ya /
T02D1946:73a-12: ya kshe yatstsha ni r'a ma ya /
T02D1946:73a-13: hu'um h'um h'um phat phat sv'a h'a /
T02D1946:73a-14: 'dis ni dngos grub chen po yang thob par 'gyur ro //
T02D1946:73a-15: aom hr'i: shtri: wi kri t'a na na h'um h'um phat phat sv'a h'a /
T02D1946:73a-17: ha cang drag min dal ba min //
T02D1946:73a-18: cung zad ring ba ma yin te //
T02D1946:73a-19: thung dang mi gsal rnams spangs te //
T02D1946:73a-20: tshig gi bar du ma chod pa'i //
T02D1946:73a-22: 'di ni bsgrub pa'i don du byas //
T02D1946:73a-23: las kun bla ma brgyud shes bya //
T02D1946:73a-24: mi shes pa dag dgrol ba'i phyir //
T02D1946:73a-25: bdag gis rtogs par gyur pa brtsams //
T02D1946:73a-27: dpal ldan gshin rje gshed 'gyur shog / sangs rgyas gshen rje gshed nag po'i sgrub thabs /
T02D1946:73a-28: n'a da ku be ra las byung ba'i don /
T02D1946:73a-29: kun da nakshe ri na bzhugs pa'i mkhas pa chen
T02D1946:73a-30: po rnal 'byor pa nag po zhabs kyis mdzad pa
